      name: "p",
      components: components
    }, `I caught myself readily dozing at my desk. At times, I would even grab a pillow and indulge in a full-fledged nap. On waking, the sounds of cicadas filled my ears. Their chirping, which carried like a call from the greater world outside, would suddenly overwhelm me. I'd listen intently, sometimes struck by a keen sense of loneliness.`), React.createElement(MDXTag, {
      name: "p",
